Screenshot 1 ‚Äì Replit

The first image shows the Replit website.

Replit is an online coding platform.

What is Replit used for?

Instead of installing Python on your laptop, you can write and run code online.

Example:

app.py
requirements.txt
main.py

You click Run, and Replit hosts your application.

It provides a public URL such as:

https://myproject.replit.app

That URL can be called from other applications like Voiceflow.

