Capture Response

The screenshot shows:

response.thread_id

This means Voiceflow stores part of the API response into a variable.

Example API response:

{
  "thread_id": "abc123",
  "message": "Welcome!"
}

Voiceflow saves:

thread_id = abc123

and can reuse it later.

